{
  "stem": "6258.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that attempt to assassinate Hitler, attempt that was in vain, we somehow knew that Plaszow cannot be long as a camp, because we heard rumors that the Russian front is moving so fast that they are supposedly on the Vistula River, and we're very close, come here.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we knew that they are preparing, and in the meantime, different things happened in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First of all, that lager elder and all the other people around him were shot by Amon Goeth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They knew too much, and he knew too much about them, and they knew that Amon Goeth stole so many things from Plaszow and, instead of sending them to Berlin, he sent them to Czechoslovakia for himself.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So anyway, we couldn't believe but it was true.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Amon Goeth was arrested and taken out of that camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we had to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew that they were sending men's transport to Gross-Rosen first and then--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then, first the men were sent away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my brother was still staying in with the hospital in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then there was a transport for women.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And actually, I did not have to go to this transport, but I didn't want to left my mother and my sister-in-law by themselves.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I asked to be written to this transport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And OK, I went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that person, that Buttner, who was the head of the clinic, he signed my name to this list.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By train, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody was counting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was not too many.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were cattle cars, and we had enough space to comfortably sit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was about quite a few hours, although it shouldn't be because Auschwitz is not so far away from Krakau.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that we are going to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
